* build puppetmaster container with:

    docker build -t lluis/puppetmaster puppetmaster/

* run puppetmaster container with:

    docker run -d --name puppetmaster -h puppet -p 8140:8140 -v `pwd`/puppetmaster/conf:/etc/puppet -v `pwd`/puppetmaster/var:/var/lib/puppet lluis/puppetmaster

* build puppetdb container with:

    docker build -t lluis/puppetdb puppetdb/

* run puppetdb container with:

    docker run -d --name puppetdb -h puppetdb -p 8080:8080 -p 8081:8081 -v `pwd`/puppetdb/conf:/etc/puppetdb lluis/puppetdb
